  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2023-05-18",
    "date": "2023-12-06T15:54:51Z",
    "text": "Protect Older Job Applicants Act of 2023 or the POJA Act of 2023\n\nThis bill prohibits employers from limiting, segregating, or classifying job applicants based on an applicant's age. It also requires the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission to study and report on claims received from job applicants involving age discrimination."
